# ==============================================================================
#  Title: Analyze TCGA mRNA Expression
#  2026-06-29 | Shiwoo Koak | Seoul National University
#
#  Description:
#    Analyze TCGA mRNA expression between matched tumor and normal samples,
#    compare expression across normal, driver-mutant tumor, and driver-WT tumor
#    groups, and create gene-gene expression scatter plots. RNA-seq and SNV
#    inputs are generated by 01_download_tcga.R.
